The paper focuses on detecting physical attacks on neural networks, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also uses techniques from model interpretability and object detection, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
